docstring.long_description:
Logs CAN data to an ASAM Measurement Data File v4 (.mf4).
The MF4 Writer does not support append mode.
A writer must be created and connected to this block before any data can be written to it, use `MF4_CREATE_WRTIER` to do so.
docstring.short_description: Write a message to a MF4 writer.

parameters.name: MF4_writer
parameters.description: A mf4 writer object from a MF4_CREATE_WRITER block.

parameters.name: messages
parameters.description: A list of message in the python-can format.
